01:09:17,700 --> 01:09:19,200
Mel!

567
01:09:35,500 --> 01:09:37,000
I’m not afraid of you.

568
01:09:39,000 --> 01:09:41,300
You’re afraid I could win her back.

569
01:09:45,900 --> 01:09:47,700
