587
01:12:56,300 --> 01:12:58,300
Meet me halfway, Ryan.

588
01:13:21,100 --> 01:13:22,800
Grandpa took the leap.

589
01:13:26,100 --> 01:13:27,800
Did he make it?

590
01:13:43,100 --> 01:13:46,700
He made it, Ryan. 
