but offer two stumps for hands.

593
01:14:21,100 --> 01:14:22,700
What a man.

594
01:14:23,900 --> 01:14:25,300
What a man.

595
01:15:34,000 --> 01:15:35,600
Dad?

596
01:15:44,100 --> 01:15:45,900
I wanted to tell you so much.

597
01:15:51,800 --> 01:15:53,600
Remember when you showed me the man in the moon?

598
01:15:54,300 --> 01:15:56,100
And I couldn’t see him for the longest time.

599
