609
01:16:52,400 --> 01:16:54,100
Dad...

610
01:16:57,600 --> 01:16:59,600
He looked so real.

611
01:17:02,200 --> 01:17:04,600
They’re waiting for us.

612
01:17:08,000 --> 01:17:09,300
Come on.

613
01:17:18,700 --> 01:17:23,600
He’d have caught me if I'd done nothing 
but offer two stumps for arms.

614
01:17:25,400 --> 01:17:28,100
What a man .... 
what a man ...

615
01:17:40,300 --> 01:17:43,500
Come on. This is supposed to be 
a celebration, remember?

616
01:17:50,400 --> 01:17:52,900
A toast, to Grandpa.

617
01:17:55,300 --> 01:17:57,200
Not here.

618
01:18:00,600 --> 01:18:03,000
I’m not sure I understand 
anything Grandpa said.

619
01:18:05,800 --> 01:18:07,500
But at least I'm not afraid anymore.

620
01:18:12,500 --> 01:18:14,200
I figure he's in eternity.

621
01:18:16,200 --> 01:18:20,700
