But then it slips away. 

622
01:18:23,400 --> 01:18:25,300
Maybe because I'm just a kid.

623
01:18:29,400 --> 01:18:30,900
Fill it up.

624
01:18:35,900 --> 01:18:39,400
To a wise old man, 
