the colors and the leaves.

705
01:33:09,800 --> 01:33:11,500
Boy, someone snowed 
you over but good.

706
01:33:14,600 --> 01:33:16,000
Come on, Ryan.

707
01:33:17,700 --> 01:33:20,200
