710
01:33:38,500 --> 01:33:40,300
So?

711
01:33:41,000 --> 01:33:42,900
Your friend can call it.

712
01:34:15,400 --> 01:34:19,800
Dust is a funny thing. 
It's everywhere all at once,

713
01:34:21,000 --> 01:34:25,500
like a teeny, tiny snowstorm, 
in every ray of light.

714
01:34:25,900 --> 01:34:29,500
Even the moon is just 
a big dust ball.

715
01:34:29,500 --> 01:34:32,200
But you know, it's all 
in the way you look at it.

716
01:34:32,300 --> 01:34:36,900
Not this way or that way, 
not forways or backways.

717
01:34:38,900 --> 01:34:41,900
Just believe before you look.

718
01:34:43,000 --> 01:34:48,200
The man in the moon 
has a magic all his own.

